ygData.msgSnippet: Warbone chips don t make you a stronger pet, they simply summon you the strongest available pet you can summon with that spell.Example:With the the level 20
ygData.messageBody:
Warbone chips don't make you a stronger pet, they simply summon you the
strongest available pet you can summon with that spell.Example:With the the
level 20 pet spell, your pet can be anywhere from 16-19.Using warbone chips,
you would summon a level 19 pet.
